flowchart LR
    classDef query fill:#E3F2FD,stroke:#1A237E,stroke-width:1.5px,color:#1A237E
    classDef store fill:#F3E5F5,stroke:#6A1B9A,stroke-width:1.5px,color:#4A148C
    classDef weak fill:#FFEBEE,stroke:#C62828,stroke-width:1.5px,color:#B71C1C
    classDef strong fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#2E7D32,stroke-width:1.5px,color:#1B5E20
    classDef llm fill:#FFFDE7,stroke:#F57F17,stroke-width:1.5px,color:#3E2723

    subgraph CLASSICAL[Classical RAG: flat semantic retrieval]
        direction LR
        CQ[User Query]:::query --> CE[Embedding]:::query --> CV[(Vector Index)]:::store --> CC[Text Chunks]:::weak --> CL[LLM Answer]:::llm
    end

    subgraph GRAPH[Graph RAG: semantic + relational retrieval]
        direction LR
        GQ[User Query]:::query --> GE[Entity Extraction]:::query --> KG[(Knowledge Graph)]:::store
        KG --> GA[Entity A]:::strong --> GR1[Typed Relation]:::strong --> GB[Entity B]:::strong --> GR2[Typed Relation]:::strong --> GC[Entity C]:::strong
        GQ --> VS[Vector Search]:::query --> EV[Evidence Chunks]:::strong
        GC --> GL[Grounded Answer]:::llm
        EV --> GL
    end
